<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="kr">

<head>
	<meta charset="utf8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<link rel="shortcut icon" href="/image/logo.png">
	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.js"></script>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css"
		integrity="sha384-JcKb8q3iqJ61gNV9KGb8thSsNjpSL0n8PARn9HuZOnIxN0hoP+VmmDGMN5t9UJ0Z" crossorigin="anonymous">
	<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"
		integrity="sha384-B4gt1jrGC7Jh4AgTPSdUtOBvfO8shuf57BaghqFfPlYxofvL8/KUEfYiJOMMV+rV" crossorigin="anonymous">
	</script>
	
	
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/post_style.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
	<title>게시글 보기</title>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="container-fluid">
		<!-- 상단 헤더 -->
		<nav class="navbar navbar-light bg-light sticky-top">
			<a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
				<img src="/image/logo.png" width="30" height="30" class="d-inline-block align-top" alt="로고"
					loading="lazy">
			</a>
		</nav>

		<!-- 점보트론 -->
		<div class="jumbotron jumbotron-fluid">
			<div class="container">
				<h1 class="display-4 text-center">창원대 이어살기</h1>
				<p class="lead text-center">창원대학교 원룸 양도 서비스입니다</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="container">
			<div class="form-group row">
				<div class="col-sm-8 post_title">
					<h1><%=result[0].title%></h1>
					<p><%=getTag(tag[0]) %></p>
				</div>
				<div class="col-sm-4 text-right">
					<% if((auth_check.login == true && auth_check.post_owner == true) || auth_check.admin == true) { %>
						<input type="hidden" value="<%=result[0].post_idx %>" name="post_idx">
						<button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-edit">수정</button>
						<button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-delete">삭제</button>
					<% } %>
					<p> <%=time[0].post_date %></p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<hr>
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-sm-2 content sub_title">연락처</div>
				<div class="col-sm-10 content"><%=result[0].contact%></div>
			</div>
			<div class="row mt-2">
				<div class="col-sm-2 content sub_title">보증금</div>
				<div class="col-sm-2 content"><%=result[0].deposit%></div>
			</div>
			<div class="row mt-2">
				<div class="col-sm-2 content sub_title">월세</div>
				<div class="col-sm-2 content"><%=result[0].monthly_rent%></div>
			</div>
			<div class="row mt-2">
				<div class="col-sm-2 content sub_title">계약기간</div>
				<div class="col-sm-10 content"><%=result[0].contract_period%></div>
			</div>
			<div class="row mt-2">
				<div class="col-sm-2 content sub_title">위치</div>
				<div class="col-sm-10 content"><%=result[0].address%></div>
			</div>
			<div class="row mt-2">
				<div class="col-sm-2 content sub_title">옵션</div>
				<div class="col-sm-10 funiture">
					<div class="row">
						<% if(result[0].air_conditioner == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_airConditioner.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  에어컨
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].refrigerator == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_refrigerator.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  냉장고
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].washing_machine == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_washer.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  세탁기
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].gas_stove == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_gasStove.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  가스레인지
							</div>						
						<% } %>

						<% if(result[0].microwave == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_microwave.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  전자레인지
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].door_lock == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_doorLock.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  도어락
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].bed == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_bed.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  침대
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].closet == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_closet.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  옷장
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].desk == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_desk.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  책상
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].wifi == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_wifi.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  와이파이
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].tv == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_TV.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  티비
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].elevator == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_elevator.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  엘리베이터
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].cctv == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_CCTV.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  CCTV
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].public_washing_machine == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_sharedWasher.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  공용세탁기
							</div>
						<% } %>
						
						<% if(result[0].public_kitchen == '1') { %>
							<div class="col-sm-2 col-xs-3 mb-2">
								<img src="/image/icon/icon_text_sharedKitchen.png" alt="" style="width: 64px; height:  64px;">
								<br/>  공용주방
							</div>
						<% } %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<hr>
			<div class="post_content">
				<p>
					<%-result[0].content %>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<footer class="text-muted border-top">
		<div class="container mt-4 pb-4">
			<p class="float-right">
				<a href="#">위로 가기</a>
			</p>
			<p>창원대학교 원룸 양도 서비스</p>
			<p>버그를 발견하셨나요? cynxia90@gmail.com로 알려주시면 감사하겠습니다!</p>
		</div>
	</footer>
	<script src="/edit_delete_button.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
